 Aye, dost  thou hate me then? O brightest 
Venus, Now or  never  make thy blind Son see; 
and wound his heart, whose hate hath wounded me.

Mark you Sir, I teach both substance and meaning; 
 I  do  not teach as your common people, d, o, b, o, b, b, bottles; 
Go sit you  down again  Tobyas. Timothie, 
come  ye  hither Timothie: How construe you this 
 verse Timothie? Iam, iam, Tacturus, Sidera summa putes
